  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.9">
<l>amarar muḻumuta lākiya vātiyai</l>
<l>yamarark kamutīnta vāyar koḻuntai</l>
<l>yamara vaḻumpat tuḻāviyeṉ ṉāvi</l>
<l>yamarat taḻuviṟ ṟiṉiya kalumō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The beginning who became the whole base of the immortals,</l>
<l>the sprout of the cowherders who gave the ambrosia to the immortals</l>
<l>my soul, stirring to be closely intimate with him,</l>
<l>embraced abiding [with him]. Now wil there be leaving?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
